# HeroUI Native Screens

## Patterns

- Use HeroUI compound components as documented (e.g. `Card` + slots, field groups).
- Interactive handlers: `onPress`, not `onClick`.
- Keep route files in `src/app` thin - compose UI; put fetch/mock calls in `src/mocks/services` or feature modules.

## Styling

- Prefer semantic tokens: `bg-background`, `text-foreground`, `bg-accent` / `text-muted` from theme.
- Uber neutrals are the visual target (black/white accent); do not reintroduce Spotify green `#1DB954` or old FlipSentry `#009966`.

## Native gaps

- Maps / MapView → placeholder image + label.
- IAP / payments → buttons + mock success/fail UI only.
- Live feed → mock list + pull-to-refresh fixtures.

## Imports

```tsx
// ✅ Pro or OSS native
import { Button, Card } from "heroui-native";
import { Stepper } from "heroui-native-pro";

// ❌ Web packages / old app stack
// import { Button } from "@heroui/react";
// import { View } from "@/components/ui/…" // mobile-app shadcn
```
